  "Jonas Senizergues, ENS Cachan (internship at AIST)"
  "Jacques Garrigue, Nagoya U."
  "Kazuhiko Sakaguchi, Tsukuba U."
  "Taku Asai, Nagoya U. (M2)"
  "Takafumi Saikawa, Nagoya U."
  "Naruomi Obata, Titech (M2)"
]
